Thank you for choosing to use Egern (“the App”). We are committed to protecting your personal privacy and data. This Privacy Policy aims to transparently explain how we handle your information and the rights and choices you have when using our App. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully.
1. Information We Collect
​
Egern is dedicated to protecting your privacy. The App does not collect, store, or transmit any of your personal information in any form. This means we do not track your device usage, location information, browsing habits, or any other data directly related to you.
2. Use of Data
​
As Egern does not collect any personal data, there is no usage of your personal data to speak of.
3. Third-Party Services
​
The App may link to third-party websites or services, such as third-party integrations or external services, that we do not own or control. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties, and we encourage you to read their privacy policies.
4. Security
​
We place a high priority on the security of your information. Given that we do not collect any personal information, there is no risk of any personal data being stored or exposed.
5. Children’s Privacy
​
The App does not target children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under 13.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
​
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page and will be communicated to you before the changes become effective.
7. Contact Us
​
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
